Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗 扇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我有责任让大家避难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我对不起你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们卷入Freyja所支配的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托瓦密舰队被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战计划继续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Avalon就这样后退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持和Damocles的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各部队以波状攻击 让Damocles继续发射Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样简单就…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 下一次发射准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战术没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只要进入腹地 就用不了Freyja了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blaze Luminous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么巨大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles原本就是为了掌握 绝对制空权而制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它再继续提升高度 我们会束手无策的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 能突破那防守吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在试 但是跟对方功率差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这状态下应该发射不了Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这边的攻击没用 就跟旁观没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界只能在Freyja压倒性的恐怖中沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是所谓和平状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,残存兵力以Avalon为中心集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同人质对Damocles发动突击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既然回来了 就说明已经有眉目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过之后还要看陛下和朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔 你打算连同人质一起消灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在黑骑士团已经败退了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就等十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才十分钟?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是已经取得反击位置了才联系我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 十分钟是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把下一弹发射前所必须的十分钟 卖了个高价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做好战后处理的准备而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说黑骑士团已经没用了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为集合体的军事力量有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们学生会成员以世界为敌作战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是挖苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我没能保护妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经很努力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑骑士团?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要亲手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕过来了吗 星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不让你击落Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻 在此止步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这违背情理之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种状态竟能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已丑陋到舍弃国家 只执着于地位了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只期望明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你期望的那是什么明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一浮空装置受损
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受损率75%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会坠落吗 这Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着慢着慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 给我们的因缘做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是有志气的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让他们进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成白刃战就有胜机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压制动力控制和通信系统 去救人质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑到这里就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰就此降落太平洋上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去执行Apate．Aletheia任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里能发射吗 Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经张开了Blaze Luminous 到临界点之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 虽然是让黑骑士团消失的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我个人的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是尤菲米娅殿下的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我必须去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个的最终程式 必须输入环境资料才能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才的话中我已理解了你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你能协助我这尤菲的仇敌 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会原谅ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许一辈子都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 另一方面 我必须找到自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真稀奇 你在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是重要的战力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我来取那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 麻烦你护卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许要亲手攻击娜娜莉也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她成为零之镇魂曲的障碍也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 你不恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为GEASS 大大改变了你的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像你啊 明明是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 因为有你给我的GEASS…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有你 我才能迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后的事 一切都由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次碰到你这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我 你去Damocles
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对手是红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心 你在担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 然后回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要给我笑容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一步棋 无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方Knightmare编队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先锋是蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将Freyja发射口的Blaze Luminous部份解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准目标改为蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 最后要舍命一击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标变更完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 修奈泽尔皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blaze Luminous解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 输入资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja每一时刻结构都会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要破坏对应其结构的反应 Freyja的临界反应就会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 必须在离爆炸约19秒时 把现场环境资料登录程式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而就算程式完成 实行时间也只有0.04秒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原理上应该是可行的 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,19秒和0.04秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然准备了这种玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破Blaze了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α3有敌机侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钥匙 Damocles的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,δ区通信断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六浮空装置控制室被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起啊 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然逼我用最后的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要用那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Damocles 已成为捕捉鲁路修他们的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们脱离后 用Freyja将Damocles整个消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会喜欢吗 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles要是上了卫星轨道 就算是Lancelot也束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赢就必须压制修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在分析内部构造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密码的阻截…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉诺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 我不承认你的布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这力量是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有必须打倒的敌人和必须拯救的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉诺 无论如何都要一战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 为了我心中要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要守护的东西 我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护?什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔在管制指令层吗 还是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja起爆位置 变更为Damocles本体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles和Freyja 终究都是机械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再造就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 托洛莫机关没这种余力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗森堡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在全世界都是鲁路修的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是消灭鲁路修的系统 各种组织都会乐意制造Freyja给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是恐怖主义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也问问娜娜莉殿下的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要吧 诱饵的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道您要抛弃她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界和平与一条生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然悲哀 但这是不能比较的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钥匙 钥匙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须阻止哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是桥头堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在阁下作战成功之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌现在的鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight Of Six
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相称的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不为国家 不为复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有丝毫野心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有战斗理由的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别搅进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由我有 就是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说你喜欢鲁路修?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过想结束经验的积累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会说人话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不亏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 是你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然还会在意胜负…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钥匙 钥匙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须阻止哥哥才行 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和胡尔特葛籣卿汇合地点是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正等着你呢 修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 被将军的是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告诉我吗 为什么会知道我的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是策略 我所看穿的是你的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本质?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没打算获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱禁城的对局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑骑士团的政变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是站在不会输的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你就知道我要放弃Damocles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔 这次你一定得输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是 杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洪古从第三通道压制舰桥 各国代表的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天子陛下 您平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻大人 我们是你们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们背叛了鲁路修?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是被威胁的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 既然鲁路修已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不再是独裁者的意义上 应该能信任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 决战似乎缩小到Damocles内部了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇先生…事务总长也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 他们都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 皇兄没有杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇兄没有执着的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若生而逢时 应能成为不凡的王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有看穿这点 是我太愚蠢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还这样称呼我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想提个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想用Damocles来掌控世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想创造大家都期望的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使无视人的本质?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们见解相异
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想将世界固定在今日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 没有变化的日常称不上生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是经验而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 经验的累积就是知识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过优秀而看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 皇帝查尔斯追求的是昨日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你追求的是今日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想要的是明日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日或许会比今日更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无论要花多少时间 人都会不断追求幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这分明就是欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不过是感情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为希望和梦想的不可靠的虚构
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在皇族的符号之下 俯视世界的你的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与不幸抗争的人 和追求未来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都期望着幸福 不断挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEASS和面具 其根源就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自相矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直否定他人意志的你 事到如今却要肯定人的意志的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 你也会被Freyja消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们的生命 换来世界的和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 送你一句话 侍奉ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从一开始就不是要杀我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何没能察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是看穿了修奈泽尔思考的录影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听凭您的吩咐 ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔 认定自己会被杀的想法 招致了你的败北
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你的故事已经完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能再活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有否定我存在的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己的生命都无所依恋的人竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是GEASS的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 至少在最后 对我也施以GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈尔特 你没有施加GEASS的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 修奈泽尔 首先解除Damocles的自爆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 Freyja的控制开关在娜娜莉手上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论机体如何强化 你都赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是结果 吉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的任务已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Blaze Luminous系统?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 吉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 看来到了结的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的目的是Damocles的钥匙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那对你来说太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再避开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破了那家伙的GEASS?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 也会对我用GEASS吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许从那天开始 我就一直迷茫着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,厌倦了这毫无改变的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是就是无法对自己撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 名字也 经历也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,得到的力量也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是让我得到真实 所需要的路标而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我一直在追求的正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
